# UniSafe Reddit OAuth Configuration
# 
# To set up your Reddit app:
# 1. Go to https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
# 2. Click "Create App" or "Create Another App"
# 3. Fill in the details:
#    - Name: UniSafe (or any name you prefer)
#    - App type: web app
#    - Description: UniFi firmware update scanner
#    - About URL: https://unisafe.tsew.com/about
#    - Redirect URI: https://unisafe.tsew.com/auth/callback
# 4. After creating, copy the Client ID and Secret below

# Your Reddit app Client ID (the string under the app name)
VITE_REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_reddit_client_id_here

# Your Reddit app Secret (the "secret" field)
VITE_REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_reddit_client_secret_here

# Note: For local development, the app will automatically use localhost URLs
# For production (unisafe.tsew.com), it will use the production URLs
